---

 Final goal (same as original problem)

From all possible harmonious bands:

> Find the band with the maximum number of singers

Here:

 Band `{9, 10}` â†’ size `2`
 Band `{12, 13, 14}` â†’ size `3`

ðŸ‘‰ Maximum size = 3

---

 ðŸ§  One-line takeaway

> Pick the largest group where everyone is on the same pitch or just one pitch apart.

